gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T18:28:33.000Z","msg":"我真係好想搬<br />\n就算係俾人領養<br />\n我都唔使要呢個阿媽"},{"pid":"f446448350ec4a94936a5cdf8ca40abc881210ae","tid":2430190,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T18:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27129022c2dc164e0ca1b583c3b95b744b753840","tid":2430190,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T18:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港有幾多人感同身受"},{"pid":"7c5120e410ce737d9468b4e31753c5b521772abc","tid":2430190,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T18:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586ffc687fbeda02f4639f9a790fd5051020123c","tid":2430190,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T18:31:10.000Z","msg":"Too long didn&rsquo;t read ？"},{"pid":"7790eb8b482d8ed2daafdead846bee407cb55b43","tid":2430190,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T18:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a156d10be084b68667bd0c155885993ad3cee5bf","tid":2430190,"uid":197852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T18:33:04.000Z","msg":"Daddy又話連登仔無咁早訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢明明係數學家<br />\n最叻計吓連登仔幾點訓"},{"pid":"62e7cd33c83c4753c707a633ac1c5783e803a940","tid":2430190,"uid":197852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T18:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />斷腳都冇人理<br />\n我同icon一樣無腳條條揈"},{"pid":"c1b8cfecf532fb1f6b88256923cc02454fadf19f","tid":2430190,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T18:35:33.000Z",